data.description: Welcome home to this hidden gem in the golf-cart friendly neighborhood of Harbor Bluffs! Just minutes from Florida’s top beaches, some of the highest rated restaurants, and downtown Tampa, you will truly be living the Florida lifestyle. The property is on a high elevation and DOES NOT REQUIRE FLOOD INSURANSE. This 4 bedroom 4 bathroom home is situated on an oversized fenced-in corner lot with beautiful professional landscaping and trees for privacy. It also features a large pool, an outdoor gazebo for entertaining, and an oversized deck for all of your gathering needs. As you enter in through the double front doors, you are embraced by the spacious foyer which opens into the living room. Centrally located in the living room is a large stone gas fireplace for the perfect ambiance. There are double sets of glass sliding doors which lead into the outdoor deck and pool area which give the perfect amount of natural light. The kitchen is conveniently located just off the living room. The stainless-steel appliances bring elegance into the home, along with the gas stove and hood, beautiful wooden cabinets, and spacious countertops. There is also an extended breakfast bar which can seat six comfortably. This kitchen is an entertainers dream and perfect for hosting. The large master bedroom features an attached bathroom with a double vanity, huge walk in closet, and a beautiful walk in shower. The additional three guest bedrooms are located in their own separate wing of the home and are all spacious with plenty of storage space. The outside area features a large in-ground pool, a giant wooden deck, space for outdoor dining, and a large pergola. You will not leave this area during the summer days and fall nights! This open concept home features high vaulted ceilings, freshly painted walls, a new air conditioning unit for the master bedroom, and a new flat metal roof. Don’t miss your chance to make this home your dream home today!
